UPDATE public.records SET form_data = '{"items":[{"clause":"4.1","requirement":"Understanding the Organization and its context","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"1)","requirement":"Have you determine external and internal issues in the Quality management system (QMS)?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"2)","requirement":"Does this issues are relevant to its purpose and ability to achieve intended outcome of to take Quality management system (QMS)?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"3)","requirement":"Have you considered the context of the organization’s overall business activities? Does QMS scope cover all the activities or any exclusion for any areas or functions?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"4.2","requirement":"Understanding the needs and expectations of interested parties","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"4.3","requirement":"Determining the scope of the Quality management system","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Have you determining this scope of the organization and considered external and internal issues?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"Do you considered any requirement of interested parties in the scope?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Have you considered interfaces and dependencies between activities perform by the organization and other organization?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"4.4","requirement":"Quality management system and its process","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"5.1","requirement":"Leadership and Commitment","finding":"C","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Does the Top Management have signed and establish an quality policy? Does he approved QMS objectives? Is he active in formulation of quality policy and Objectives? Does the QMS objectives are in line with strategic direction of the organization?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"How do you ensure the integration of the Quality management system requirement with the organization Processes?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"How do you ensure resources related to Quality management systems (QMS are available? If any resources are lacking then whom do you contact? What is a formal process for getting approval of resources? How do you carry out capacity planning and budget approval to get management approval for resources related to Quality management system?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"d)","requirement":"Have you communicated in the organization related QMS system requirements?  How do you communicate the importance of effective Quality management system implementation and benefits? What is the methods followed for communication?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"e)","requirement":"How do you ensure QMS achieves its intended outcome","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"f)","requirement":"How many people are directing and supporting to contribute the effectiveness of QMS system? Have you define QMS Supporting Team?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"g)","requirement":"How do you promote for continual improvement?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"h)","requirement":"What are the roles of the management? How do you support and demonstrate leadership for QMS? How do you demonstrate your leadership and commitment for ISO 9001 QMS system?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"5.2","requirement":"Policy","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"5.3","requirement":"Organizational roles, responsibilities and authorities","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"6.1","requirement":"Action to address risks and opportunities","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"How do you ensure the Quality management system can achieve its intended outcome?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"How do you prevent, or reduce, undesired effects related to risk?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"How do you achieve continual improvement?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"6.2","requirement":"Quality objectives  and Planning to achieve them","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"6.3","requirement":"Planning of changes","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"7.1","requirement":"Resources","finding":"C","status":""},{"clause":"7.2","requirement":"Competence","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Does the organisation determine necessary competence for personnel performing activities affecting QMS? How do you determine competency? Do you prepare the competency matrix related to QMS activity?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Have you ensure that the necessary competence has been achieved? If any areas the competency is not achieved then what action is taken?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"Do you provide training or take other actions to achieve the necessary competence? Have you define what is appropriate education, training and experience for different category of persons? Where do you maintain such documented information?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Have you ensure that the necessary competence has been achieved? What actions are taken to acquire the necessary competence? How do you evaluate the effectiveness of action taken for example written test, mock trail, review of effectiveness of training etc? What action was taken to upgrade the competence of people?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"d)","requirement":"Are you maintaining appropriate information and documented information of education, training, skills and experience and qualifications as an evidence of competence?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"7.3","requirement":"Awareness","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Do your employees are aware of quality policy and Quality objective? How do you contribute your work to implement the quality policy in your work area?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"How do you contribute to Quality management system? What benefits are achieved by implementing the QMS? What is your improved quality performance?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Does the employee aware for what is the implication of not conforming with QMS requirements and for not fulfilling Quality obligations? How do you provide such awareness to all concern persons?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"7.4","requirement":"communication","finding":"C","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"What do you communicate related QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"When do you communicate related QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Whom do you communicate related QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"d)","requirement":"How do you communicate related QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"e)","requirement":"Who will communicate related QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"7.5","requirement":"Documented Information","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"7.5.1","requirement":"General","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Do you require information documented as per ISO 9001:2015?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"How do you decide the need of the effective documentation information?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Do you documented requirement Paper copy or electronic copy?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"1)","requirement":"What is your documented information for competence of person?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"2)","requirement":"Have you documented related like quality policy and QMS objectives?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"3)","requirement":"Have you documented scope of the QMS?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"5)","requirement":"Have you any documented information compliance to ISO 9001:2015 requirements?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"7.5.2","requirement":"Creating and Updating","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Have you created and updated documented information covering  proper identification and description of the title, date, author or reference number?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"Do you made format for documented information including identification, language, software version, and graphics and media like paper copy and electronic copy?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Who is  reviewing and updating  and re-approved documented, information?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"d)","requirement":"Have you approved information for adequacy and suitability prior to issue ? Who is authorized to approve and review the documented information? How do you ensure documented information is adequate and suitable for the purpose? Where did you defined such authority for approval and review of documented information","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"7.5.3","requirement":"Control of documented information","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"a)","requirement":"Have you defined any control mechanism for documented information? How do you ensure documented information is available for use when it is required?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"b)","requirement":"How do you protect documented information?  How do you adopt system like confidentiality, improper use, or loss of integrity?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"c)","requirement":"Does the documents required by the QMS is protected and controlled? How? Who is authorised to control QMS documents? How do you distribute the documented information? Have you prepared authorized copy holder list to understand who is having access of information? How do you retrieve documented information and use it?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"d)","requirement":"Are documented information established and maintained to provide evidence of conformity to requirements and the effective operation of the QMS? How do you store and preserve the documented information? How do you ensure it is legible?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"e)","requirement":"Is it protected and controlled?  How do you change the documented information? How do you establish version control for your documented information? Are you using any automated tool for such version control and configuration management?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"f)","requirement":"Is there a documented information define the controls needed for the identification, storage, protection, retrieval, retention time and disposition of documented information? Have you define the retention period for various types of documented information? How do you dispose of such documented information in hard copy as well as soft copy?","finding":"","status":""},{"clause":"8.1","requirement":"Operational Planning and control","finding":"C","status":""},{"clause":"8.2","requirement":"Requirements for products and services","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"8.2.1","requirement":"Customer communication","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"8.2.2","requirement":"Determining the requirements related to product & services","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"8.2.3","requirement":"Review of requirements related to the products and services","finding":"OBS","status":""},{"clause":"8.3","requirement":"Design and development of products and services","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.1","requirement":"General","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.2","requirement":"Design and development (D&D) planning","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.3","requirement":"Design and development  Inputs","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.4","requirement":"Development controls","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.5","requirement":"Design and development outputs","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8.3.6","requirement":"Design and Development changes","finding":"NA","status":""},{"clause":"8